    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《BLUE NIGHT LAUNDROMAT - 洗衣店奇遇夜》</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“这家店真的在营业吗？”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >复古风点击式逃脱冒险游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两名青年偶遇于深夜洗衣店，奋力逃出生天！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆本作与前作《PLEASE KNOCK -before entering my room-》在剧情上有所关联</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（未游玩过前作，也可游玩本作）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >概要</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・选项&amp;探索式 点击冒险+电子小说</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・所需时间：约30分钟-1小时</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・共6个成就</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・集齐全成就可解锁隐藏剧情</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・关于直播或录制视频：可以直播或录制到一周目通关为止</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・可选择中辣或辛辣模式（2024.12.30更新新增功能，仅日语版及简中版支持）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注：在辛辣模式下，部分谜题难度较高，主角口无遮拦，可能会令部分玩家反感或受到惊吓，还请注意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145540/extras/e18ae5650a5183c059b5bc95b3b3d31d.avif?t=1747970924\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145540/extras_big/e18ae5650a5183c059b5bc95b3b3d31d.avif?t=1747970924 width=800 height=720 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
